    public abstract class AppendCompactWorkerOperator<IN>
extends PrepareCommitOperator<IN,Committable>
    An abstract Operator to execute UnawareAppendCompactionTask passed from BucketUnawareCompactSource for compacting table. This operator is always in async mode.
